"Public law problem (the local council is involved)\n"
"eg care proceedings or adoption"
msgstr ""
"Problem cyfraith gyhoeddus (mae'r cyngor lleol ynghlwm) \n"
"\n"
"e.e. achosion gofal neu fabwysiadu"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:902
msgid "Typically the local council is involved due to child protection concerns."
msgstr "Yn gyffredinol, mae'r cyngor lleol ynghlwm oherwydd pryderon amddiffyn plentyn."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:916
