#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1352
msgid "The client thinks that they have been treated worse, or disadvantaged in some way, because they have brought a claim of discrimination, given evidence or information in relation to someone else’s claim of discrimination, made a complaint of discrimination, or been suspected of doing one of these things. For example, an employee is dismissed after making a discrimination claim."
msgstr "Mae'r cleient yn credu ei fod wedi cael ei drin yn waeth, neu o dan anfantais mewn rhyw ffordd, oherwydd eu bod wedi gwneud hawliad am wahaniaethu, rhoi tystiolaeth neu wybodaeth mewn perthynas â hawliad rhywun arall am wahaniaethu, wedi gwneud cwyn am wahaniaethu, neu wedi cael ei ddrwgdybio o wneud un o'r rhain. Er enghraifft, mae gweithiwr yn cael ei diswyddo ar ôl gwneud hawliad am wahaniaethu.  "

