msgstr "Nid oes gan y cleient y DDAU sef tystiolaeth o'r diffyg atgyweirio A'R rheswm dros feddwl bod y diffyg atgyweirio yn gosod risg o niwed, anaf neu salwch difrifol iddynt hwy neu eu teulu."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1783
msgid "Client is the alleged abusive partner and wants to defend an injunction. This will be in scope for Civil Legal Advice."
