#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1786
msgid ""
"Where a Client wants to seek a court order to protect themselves or a child from abuse via a court order 'an injunction' that tells a person they're not allowed to do a certain act. There are two main forms of injunction\n"
"\n"
"* A non-molestation order - aimed at preventing your partner or ex-partner from using or threatening violence against you or your child, or intimidating, harassing or pestering you, in order to ensure the health, safety and well-being of yourself and your children.\n"
"\n"
"* An occupation order can aimed at deciding who can live in the family home, and can also restrict your abuser from entering the surrounding area. If you do not feel safe continuing to live with your partner, or if you have left home because of violence, but want to return and exclude your abuser, you may want to apply for an occupation order.\n"
"\n"
"Some clients who are the alleged abuser do not agree with the injunction against them and wish to get help in defending themselves against it."
msgstr ""
"Pan fo Cleient eisiau ceisio am orchymyn llys i ddiogelu eu hunain neu blentyn rhag camdriniaeth drwy orchymyn llys sef 'gwaharddeb' sy'n dweud wrth unigolyn nad oes ganddynt hawl i wneud gweithred bendodol. Mae dau brif fath o waharddeb:\n"
"\n"
"* Gorchymyn rhag molestu - wedi ei anelu at atal eich partner neu gyn bartner rhag defnyddio neu fygwth defnyddio trais yn eich erbyn neu eich plentyn, neu eich bygwth, aflonyddu neu eich poeni, er mwyn sicrhau iechyd, diogelwch a lles eich hunain a'ch plant.\n"
"\n"
"* Gall gorchymyn anheddu anelu at wneud penderfyniad ynghylch pwy all fyw yng nghartref y teulu, a hefyd gall gyfyngu eich camdriniwr rhag dod i'r ardal gyfagos. Os nad ydych yn teimlo'n ddiogel i barhau i fyw gyda'ch partner, neu eich bod wedi gadael eich cartref oherwydd trais, ond eisiau dychwelyd a chau eich camdriniwr allan, efallai y dylech wneud cais am orchymyn anheddu.\n"
"\n"
"Nid yw rhai cleientiaid sy'n gadriniwyr honedig yn cytuno ar y waharddeb yn eu herbyn ac yn dymuno cael cymorth i'w amddiffyn eu hunain yn ei erbyn."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1806
msgid "The client is being harassed by a partner, ex-partner or family member"
msgstr "Mae partner, cynbartner neu aelod o'r teulu yn aflonyddu'r cleient."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1809
msgid "Seeking protection from a partner, ex partner or other family member due to a fear of violence or unwanted behaviour which is causing them alarm or distress. Also covers client who have previously taken action to stop harassment (i.e. sought an injunction) but this is not being complied with."
