msgid "The client has not been identified as homeless through a Community Care Assessment"
msgstr "Nid yw'r cleient wedi cael ei ddynodi yn ddigartref drwy Asesiad Gofal Cymunedol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2234
msgid "Client wants advice about international family maintenance"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient eisiau cyngor am gynhaliaeth teulu rhyngwladol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2237
msgid ""
"Covers enforcement of maintenance orders made outside the UK. Clients who have obtained maintenance orders in one country can apply to have them registered and enforced in another country. \n"
"\n"
"So where a client wants to obtain an order outside the UK this will not be in scope.\n"
"\n"
"**NOTE: These are very unusual cases.**"
msgstr ""
"Mae'n ymdrin â gorchmynion gorfodi cynhaliaeth a wneir y tu allan i'r DU. Gall cleientiaid sydd wedi cael gorchmynion cynhaliaeth mewn un wlad wneud cais i'w cofrestru a'u gorfodi mewn gwlad arall.\n"
"\n"
"Felly pan fydd cleient yn cael gorchymyn y tu allan i'r DU, ni fydd hyn mewn cwmpas.\n"
"\n"
"** NODYN: Mae'r rhain yn achosion anghyffredin."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2295
msgid "Not a Civil Legal Advice category or legal problem."
msgstr "Nid yw'n gategori Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil nac yn broblem gyfreithiol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2309
msgid ""
"IMPORTANT: Where a client or a child is AT IMMEDIATE RISK OF ABUSE you must follow the Civil Legal Advice Child, Young Person and Adult at Risk of Abuse Policy. You may need to report the matter to protection services.\n"
"\n"
"*Click 'Next' to continue*"
msgstr ""
"PWYSIG: Lle bo cleient neu blentyn mewn RISG O GAMDRINIAETH YN SYTH, mae'n rhaid i chi ddilyn Polisi Plentyn, Unigolyn Ifanc ac Oedolyn sydd mewn Risg o Gamdriniaeth. Efallai bydd angen i chi adrodd y mater i wasanaethau diogelu.\n"
"\n"
"* Cliciwch 'Nesaf' i barhau* "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2317
msgid "Legal advice in support of family mediation"
msgstr "Cyngor cyfreithiol i gefnogi cyfryngu teulu"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2320
msgid ""
"Family mediation can help people whose relationships have broken down to reach their own agreement about money, property and childcare, without going to court.\n"
"\n"
"If the client wants legal advice to support of ongoing or recently completed mediation process this will be in scope. This can include making any agreement reached in mediation legally binding by applying to the court (a consent order).\n"
"\n"
"*Please note: Mediation must be ongoing or have concluded. Clients will not qualify for Civil Legal Advice advice where mediation has not yet taken place or they have only attended Mediation Assessment Information Meeting (MIAM).*"
msgstr ""
"Gall cyfryngu teulu helpu pobl sydd â pherthynas sydd wedi chwalu, i ddod i gytundeb eu hunain ynghylch arian, eiddo a gofal plant heb fynd i'r llys.\n"
"\n"
"Os yw'r cleient eisiau cyngor cyfreithiol i gefnogi proses cyfryngu parhaus neu gyfryngu sydd wedi dod i ben yn ddiweddar, yna bydd hyn o fewn y cwmpas. Gall hyn gynnwys gwneud unrhyw gytundeb a ddaethpwyd iddo yn y cyfarfod cyfryngu a'i rhwymo mewn cyfraith drwy wneud cais i'r llys (gorchymyn cydsynio).\n"
"\n"
"* Sylwch: Rhaid i'r cyfryngu fod yn barhaus neu wedi dod i ben. Ni fydd cleientiaid yn gymwys am gyngor gan Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil os na fydd y cyfryngu wedi digwydd eto neu os mai dim ond Cyfarfod Cyfryngu, Gwybodaeth ac Asesu (MIAM) y maent wedi'i fynychu.*"

